1
00:00:55,000 --> 00:01:00,000
The Story of Minglan

2
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:03,080
Episode 6

3
00:01:03,599 --> 00:01:05,199
I haven't seen your Sixth Sister these years

4
00:01:05,199 --> 00:01:06,519
and she's grown up.

5
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:08,639
If she came and walked towards me,

6
00:01:08,760 --> 00:01:09,800
I wouldn't have recognized her.

7
00:01:10,760 --> 00:01:12,239
You already passed the exam,

8
00:01:12,239 --> 00:01:13,160
and even if you had planted a tree,

9
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:14,680
it would be over 6 meters tall now.

10
00:01:16,400 --> 00:01:18,599
Second Uncle, you sit in my seat.

11
00:01:18,720 --> 00:01:19,239
Alright.

12
00:01:19,319 --> 00:01:20,440
Second Uncle, you use mine.

13
00:01:20,680 --> 00:01:21,360
Brother Yuanruo,

14
00:01:21,360 --> 00:01:23,040
Why do you call him Second Uncle?

15
00:01:24,959 --> 00:01:25,959
We are relatives back up the genealogy.

16
00:01:27,559 --> 00:01:29,559
This is our Fourth Sister, Molan.

17
00:01:30,319 --> 00:01:32,040
Then I will call you Second Uncle

18
00:01:32,080 --> 00:01:33,120
As Brother Yuanruo does.

19
00:01:33,599 --> 00:01:34,160
You don't mind, do you?

20
00:01:34,360 --> 00:01:34,919
No.

21
00:01:36,160 --> 00:01:37,000
Greetings, Second Uncle.

22
00:01:40,040 --> 00:01:41,279
Greetings, Fourth Sister.

23
00:01:42,480 --> 00:01:43,559
Second Uncle Gu, greetings.

24
00:01:43,879 --> 00:01:46,080
And this is our Fifth Sister, Rulan.

25
00:01:46,440 --> 00:01:47,400
Greetings, Fifth Sister.

26
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:51,559
Everyone is here.

27
00:01:52,760 --> 00:01:54,599
Greetings to Scholar Zhuang.

28
00:01:55,160 --> 00:01:57,559
Classmate from the Gu's Marquis Manor is here too.

29
00:01:58,080 --> 00:01:59,720
Yes, he only arrived this morning

30
00:01:59,720 --> 00:02:00,720
and rushed to come here.

31
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:02,279
Good.

32
00:02:02,279 --> 00:02:03,879
A youth should be diligent in the morning.

33
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:06,040
It's never too late to start your path.

34
00:02:06,319 --> 00:02:07,480
You are right, Scholar.

35
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:08,960
Everyone, sit.

36
00:02:11,320 --> 00:02:13,279
Bring me your homework

37
00:02:13,279 --> 00:02:14,320
from past days.

38
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:15,199
Sit here.

39
00:02:17,279 --> 00:02:17,880
Second Brother Gu.

40
00:02:20,919 --> 00:02:22,119
Look at mine first, Scholar

41
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:39,839
My Third Brother is versed in old and new.

42
00:02:39,839 --> 00:02:41,000
Of course he dares to present his

43
00:02:41,039 --> 00:02:42,520
to the Scholar first!

44
00:02:43,119 --> 00:02:45,000
Versed in old and new? I think…

45
00:02:56,479 --> 00:02:57,559
At your age,

46
00:02:57,559 --> 00:02:59,279
you are able to write such an essay.

47
00:02:59,600 --> 00:03:00,800
What a rarity.

48
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:04,919
Even some candidates for the Imperial Exams wouldn't…

49
00:03:05,320 --> 00:03:07,479
Fifth Sister. Fifth Sister?

50
00:03:09,919 --> 00:03:11,000
That brush you're holding,

51
00:03:11,600 --> 00:03:12,960
it looks familiar to me.

52
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:16,759
It was yours before,

53
00:03:16,759 --> 00:03:18,240
but Sixth Sister gifted it to me.

54
00:03:18,720 --> 00:03:19,960
Such a nice item.

55
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:21,000
How could you bear to gift it away?

56
00:03:24,679 --> 00:03:25,559
The brush is nice,

57
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:27,880
but Fifth Miss, your penmanship is even better.

58
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:29,839
In your hands,

59
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:32,600
even if it's just a tree stick,

60
00:03:32,600 --> 00:03:34,160
it would still shine through the ink.

61
00:03:41,199 --> 00:03:42,199
Fifth Sister,

62
00:03:42,199 --> 00:03:43,759
can't you distinguish between satire and compliments?

63
00:03:43,839 --> 00:03:44,919
Of course you need a good brush

64
00:03:44,919 --> 00:03:46,039
to write well.

65
00:03:51,839 --> 00:03:54,080
Brother Yuanruo,

66
00:03:54,080 --> 00:03:56,600
I wonder how many more fine brushes like this you have?

67
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:58,440
Sixth Sister

68
00:03:58,440 --> 00:03:59,839
gifted me one too.

69
00:04:15,759 --> 00:04:17,519
You little chit.

70
00:04:17,519 --> 00:04:19,920
Upon meeting, you called him Second Uncle Gu.

71
00:04:20,239 --> 00:04:21,000
He's the legitimate heir

72
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:22,040
of the Marquis Manor.

73
00:04:22,239 --> 00:04:23,399
You added so much age to his address

74
00:04:23,440 --> 00:04:24,359
and it's unsuitable.

75
00:04:24,519 --> 00:04:27,079
Mother, what's unsuitable?

76
00:04:27,799 --> 00:04:30,000
If I follow my brother's address,

77
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:31,440
I need to call him Second Brother Gu.

78
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:33,720
But then Brother Yuanruo

79
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:35,440
would be a nephew a generation lower than I am.

80
00:04:36,359 --> 00:04:37,799
And that would be unsuitable.

81
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:40,600
Be that as it may,

82
00:04:40,640 --> 00:04:42,440
he's still the legitimate son of the Marquis Manor.

83
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:44,200
And you'll all be classmates,

84
00:04:44,239 --> 00:04:45,799
seeing each other daily…

85
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:46,959
Mother!

86
00:04:48,959 --> 00:04:50,600
Don't speak nonsense.

87
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:52,279
How unfavorable is it for others to hear?

88
00:04:54,359 --> 00:04:55,600
This Gu Tingye,

89
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:56,959
though he's not been at Dongjing

90
00:04:56,959 --> 00:04:57,920
these last three to five years,

91
00:04:57,920 --> 00:04:59,160
he went to White Deer Academy.

92
00:04:59,679 --> 00:05:01,720
However, I often hear my brother mention him.

93
00:05:02,640 --> 00:05:03,839
He's a

94
00:05:03,839 --> 00:05:05,920
frequent customer of the entertainment inns

95
00:05:06,679 --> 00:05:08,559
and a pampered young master of the brothels.

96
00:05:08,559 --> 00:05:10,239
If I catch his fancy,

97
00:05:11,359 --> 00:05:13,040
My life is done for forever.

98
00:05:13,839 --> 00:05:15,279
You said

99
00:05:15,279 --> 00:05:16,640
as if the Young Lord

100
00:05:16,679 --> 00:05:18,160
already vowed to marry you!

101
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:21,279
The Young Lord

102
00:05:21,279 --> 00:05:22,880
often comes to see me write lately.

103
00:05:23,320 --> 00:05:24,920
And he compliments me that my writing is nice.

104
00:05:27,320 --> 00:05:28,760
Was he looking at you,

105
00:05:28,760 --> 00:05:30,359
or the brush you're holding?

106
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:34,959
He's looking at the brush from his hand,

107
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:35,880
coming to my hand

108
00:05:35,880 --> 00:05:37,279
and writing out so nicely.

109
00:05:39,320 --> 00:05:40,679
Wouldn't he be enticed?

110
00:05:44,399 --> 00:05:45,119
My daughter

111
00:05:45,119 --> 00:05:46,959
is the best Miss of Sheng manor.

112
00:05:47,359 --> 00:05:49,079
If that Young Lord is smitten by you,

113
00:05:49,119 --> 00:05:50,440
that's nothing peculiar.

114
00:05:51,320 --> 00:05:52,799
I just don't know

115
00:05:52,799 --> 00:05:54,440
what your father is thinking though.

116
00:05:54,559 --> 00:05:55,200
Why did he let that

117
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:57,000
loafer Gu come to study?

118
00:05:57,359 --> 00:05:59,320
All the maidens of the family are there.

119
00:06:00,359 --> 00:06:02,239
What if he takes a interest in you too?

120
00:06:02,239 --> 00:06:03,799
What do we do then?

121
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:06,799
Mother, you don't worry.

122
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:10,640
That Gu Tingye is quite haughty.

123
00:06:11,440 --> 00:06:12,640
He's already said before,

124
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:14,279
that he will only marry the legitimate daughter

125
00:06:14,279 --> 00:06:15,000
of an aristocrat.

126
00:06:16,440 --> 00:06:19,320
Regrettably all the aristocratic households

127
00:06:19,320 --> 00:06:20,959
of the capital dislike his loafing badly.

128
00:06:21,399 --> 00:06:22,600
No one wants to marry

129
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:23,519
their legitimate daughter to him,

130
00:06:23,760 --> 00:06:25,320
or else at an age past twenty

131
00:06:25,320 --> 00:06:26,519
why is he still unmarried?

132
00:06:27,519 --> 00:06:28,320
Duke and Marquis households

133
00:06:28,320 --> 00:06:29,279
wanting to marry with legitimate daughters

134
00:06:29,279 --> 00:06:29,880
as wives is common.

135
00:06:30,399 --> 00:06:32,000
Gu Tingye wants a legitimate daughter,

136
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:33,239
so does this Young Lord of yours,

137
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:35,880
wouldn't he want a legitimate daughter too?

138
00:06:35,959 --> 00:06:36,519
Brother Yuanruo

139
00:06:36,519 --> 00:06:37,760
is a true gentleman.

140
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:39,040
He wouldn't commit

141
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:40,160
such an arrogant act.

142
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:45,239
Yunzai that works for me

143
00:06:45,239 --> 00:06:47,679
has had drinks with his manservant a few times.

144
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:49,799
She only heard from him after getting him drunk,

145
00:06:50,640 --> 00:06:51,720
that Brother Yuanruo

146
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:53,640
never cares about legitimate or not,

147
00:06:53,839 --> 00:06:54,920
as long as the person is nice.

148
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:57,679
He said

149
00:06:57,679 --> 00:07:00,440
that a man should earn his own honour and official rank.

150
00:07:01,200 --> 00:07:02,399
Win a noble position for one's wife and leave it to his posterity

151
00:07:02,399 --> 00:07:03,239
is what a truly great man does.

152
00:07:22,799 --> 00:07:23,440
May I ask

153
00:07:23,440 --> 00:07:25,000
if it's Young Lord who is in there?

154
00:07:29,399 --> 00:07:30,399
Miss Xiaotao?

155
00:07:32,559 --> 00:07:33,679
What brought you here?

156
00:07:34,359 --> 00:07:36,040
Young Lord, you left your book in the study hall,

157
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:37,279
so I brought it to you.

158
00:07:38,359 --> 00:07:39,200
Please wait.

159
00:07:43,640 --> 00:07:44,640
My miss said,

160
00:07:44,640 --> 00:07:46,880
Young Lord meant well.

161
00:07:46,880 --> 00:07:48,079
It's regrettable that her writing

162
00:07:48,079 --> 00:07:49,720
is so beyond help

163
00:07:49,760 --> 00:07:50,720
that such nice brushes

164
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:52,040
may go to waste with her.

165
00:07:52,119 --> 00:07:53,519
She is so sorry

166
00:07:53,519 --> 00:07:55,040
For your kindness.

167
00:07:55,399 --> 00:07:57,119
This is snack made at home

168
00:07:57,119 --> 00:07:58,320
for you to try,

169
00:07:58,399 --> 00:08:00,040
as a token of my Miss' regret.

170
00:08:00,760 --> 00:08:02,399
How could it be a waste used by her?

171
00:08:03,640 --> 00:08:05,399
It's because the writing isn't good

172
00:08:05,399 --> 00:08:06,679
that it requires a good brush.

173
00:08:07,839 --> 00:08:09,359
Or else,

174
00:08:09,359 --> 00:08:10,880
may I bring her some floral papers?

175
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:12,119
My Miss said

176
00:08:12,119 --> 00:08:14,279
Young Lord is the most merciful.

177
00:08:14,679 --> 00:08:15,880
Only if word gets out

178
00:08:15,920 --> 00:08:16,880
to the gossipers,

179
00:08:16,959 --> 00:08:18,600
it might harm your reputation.

180
00:08:19,720 --> 00:08:20,880
I'm a grown man.

181
00:08:20,880 --> 00:08:22,320
Who cares about reputation?

182
00:08:26,839 --> 00:08:28,279
She took my stuff

183
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:30,320
and threw them to others,

184
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:32,679
and then tried to fob me off like this.

185
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:34,919
Miss said

186
00:08:34,919 --> 00:08:37,479
you needn't bring anything for her in the future either.

187
00:08:37,520 --> 00:08:38,479
She's accomplished no merit

188
00:08:38,479 --> 00:08:39,799
to deserve it,

189
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:40,960
and it would only make her feel guilty.

190
00:08:41,239 --> 00:08:43,159
She would feel really uneasy.

191
00:08:43,159 --> 00:08:44,799
Young Lord, your Imperial exam is the most urgent matter.

192
00:08:44,919 --> 00:08:45,960
May you take care.

193
00:09:07,479 --> 00:09:08,559
The clerk left some fresh jasper cakes

194
00:09:08,559 --> 00:09:09,640
for us especially.

195
00:09:09,880 --> 00:09:11,119
We'll bring them to your mother

196
00:09:11,119 --> 00:09:12,200
and she'll surely be pleased.

197
00:09:18,559 --> 00:09:21,159
Young Master, where did this come from?

198
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:30,080
I keep thinking

199
00:09:30,080 --> 00:09:31,479
I am being nice to her,

200
00:09:33,559 --> 00:09:35,280
but she may not even care after all.

201
00:09:38,359 --> 00:09:39,840
Do you mean Sixth Miss Sheng?

202
00:09:48,080 --> 00:09:49,719
I am used to having my way in life.

203
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:52,479
I deemed myself so precious.

204
00:09:53,479 --> 00:09:55,280
But she didn't even care

205
00:09:55,280 --> 00:09:57,440
to talk to me much.

206
00:09:57,960 --> 00:09:59,760
Gifts I presented her?

207
00:10:00,880 --> 00:10:02,479
She just threw them to others in a blink.

208
00:10:06,239 --> 00:10:07,919
I kept thinking…

209
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:11,799
that she felt shy.

210
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:16,320
In fact she is actually

211
00:10:16,320 --> 00:10:19,200
afraid of me and tired of me.

212
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:21,200
Hiding from me.

213
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:22,239
Disregarding me.

214
00:10:23,799 --> 00:10:24,640
So it must be

215
00:10:24,640 --> 00:10:26,400
because of Sixth Miss Sheng.

216
00:10:26,559 --> 00:10:27,760
She's concubine-born,

217
00:10:27,760 --> 00:10:29,799
so why would she look down upon you?

218
00:10:29,840 --> 00:10:30,280
Young Master,

219
00:10:30,280 --> 00:10:31,679
you are the sole heir of Duke Qi.

220
00:10:34,239 --> 00:10:34,760
So if I'm a young lord,

221
00:10:34,760 --> 00:10:36,919
she must respect me?

222
00:10:37,039 --> 00:10:38,400
So what if she's concubine-born?

223
00:10:38,400 --> 00:10:39,919
She's not allowed to disregard me then?

224
00:10:42,200 --> 00:10:43,359
I was just been self-sentimental.

225
00:10:44,799 --> 00:10:45,719
Laughable.

226
00:10:48,679 --> 00:10:49,679
How laughable.

227
00:10:51,280 --> 00:10:53,039
Young Lord, you've not had wine

228
00:10:53,039 --> 00:10:54,359
but why do you look like drunk?

229
00:10:55,159 --> 00:10:56,200
I'm a bit scared.

230
00:10:57,799 --> 00:10:59,080
Sixth Miss came by earlier?

231
00:11:01,119 --> 00:11:02,239
Is this from her?

232
00:11:03,919 --> 00:11:05,119
What on earth did she say?

233
00:11:14,640 --> 00:11:15,679
Wine?

234
00:11:17,239 --> 00:11:18,159
Great.

235
00:11:19,400 --> 00:11:20,400
That's a great idea.

236
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:23,840
Turn around.

237
00:11:23,840 --> 00:11:25,239
Let's go and drink wine at Fanlou.

238
00:11:25,440 --> 00:11:26,280
Turn around.

239
00:11:30,119 --> 00:11:31,880
Young Lord, that's not a good idea.

240
00:11:32,479 --> 00:11:33,280
Her Highness is still

241
00:11:33,280 --> 00:11:34,159
waiting for you at home.

242
00:11:35,559 --> 00:11:37,119
Driver Wang, we're not turning around.

243
00:11:41,960 --> 00:11:42,880
Turn around!

244
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:44,119
Don't turn around!

245
00:11:44,640 --> 00:11:46,280
Buwei,

246
00:11:46,280 --> 00:11:47,840
you want to annoy me, too?

247
00:11:51,479 --> 00:11:52,479
Turn around!

248
00:12:01,599 --> 00:12:02,599
I already told everything you told me

249
00:12:02,599 --> 00:12:03,919
to say to Young Lord.

250
00:12:04,520 --> 00:12:06,280
Miss, you're so smart.

251
00:12:06,520 --> 00:12:07,280
How did you know

252
00:12:07,280 --> 00:12:09,280
how the Young Lord would respond?

253
00:12:09,520 --> 00:12:11,039
It was exactly as you said it would be.

254
00:12:11,799 --> 00:12:13,159
How did he look?

255
00:12:13,919 --> 00:12:16,159
At first, he was pretty anxious.

256
00:12:16,479 --> 00:12:19,320
Then he got angry.

257
00:12:20,039 --> 00:12:22,239
Then he wasn't angry again.

258
00:12:23,919 --> 00:12:25,960
It seemed he didn't want to talk to me anymore.

259
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:33,719
Being angry is also fine,

260
00:12:33,719 --> 00:12:34,880
and not wanting to talk is fine too.

261
00:12:35,359 --> 00:12:37,599
It's all fine. All fine.

262
00:12:40,599 --> 00:12:42,039
My mother just worries too much.

263
00:12:42,039 --> 00:12:43,039
Was she afraid Sheng Manor had no food

264
00:12:43,039 --> 00:12:44,119
that she insisted I come back to get it?

265
00:12:44,440 --> 00:12:45,159
It's delaying me

266
00:12:45,200 --> 00:12:46,239
and making me late.

267
00:12:46,479 --> 00:12:47,119
These jade cakes were made personally

268
00:12:47,119 --> 00:12:48,200
by Madam.

269
00:12:48,640 --> 00:12:50,159
She said you caused trouble to the Sheng's

270
00:12:50,159 --> 00:12:51,200
for studying there.

271
00:12:51,200 --> 00:12:52,679
So she wanted you to bring them to the Sheng's to try.

272
00:12:54,719 --> 00:12:55,520
Young Master.

273
00:12:56,200 --> 00:12:56,960
Nanny Xiang.

274
00:12:57,599 --> 00:12:59,200
Did you get the jade cakes?

275
00:12:59,559 --> 00:13:01,359
Madam saved them for you especially.

276
00:13:02,640 --> 00:13:04,159
You're in such a flurry.

277
00:13:04,159 --> 00:13:04,799
Where are you going?

278
00:13:06,400 --> 00:13:07,760
Nothing.

279
00:13:07,760 --> 00:13:09,559
Aren't you headed to Sheng Manor to study?

280
00:13:09,840 --> 00:13:11,640
Don't let your studies be delayed.

281
00:13:13,479 --> 00:13:14,520
What is it exactly?

282
00:13:16,799 --> 00:13:19,080
It's just some unimportant matters in backyard.

