00:24:27,800 --> 00:24:29,800
The only daughter of the Marquis of Yongyi,

566
00:24:29,839 --> 00:24:32,000
Such style and poise!

567
00:24:33,880 --> 00:24:35,079
I only hope

568
00:24:35,079 --> 00:24:37,160
to be able to meet with her again.

569
00:24:49,560 --> 00:24:50,760
When the flowers have only just bloomed

570
00:24:50,760 --> 00:24:52,040
why are you holding a fan?

571
00:24:52,680 --> 00:24:54,079
You'll look inexperienced and ignorant.

572
00:24:58,680 --> 00:25:01,359
Mother, no one is calling us yet.

573
00:25:02,760 --> 00:25:04,040
Could it be that she's not calling us?

574
00:25:07,560 --> 00:25:08,400
No such rule.

575
00:25:10,239 --> 00:25:11,359
She's the Madam,

576
00:25:11,359 --> 00:25:13,119
then she should have the demeanor of one.

577
00:25:13,239 --> 00:25:14,760
Any female guests

578
00:25:14,760 --> 00:25:16,079
would just have this request

579
00:25:16,119 --> 00:25:17,319
to have a look at the children.

580
00:25:17,880 --> 00:25:19,719
If the guest asks for it, and she doesn't call us

581
00:25:19,719 --> 00:25:21,319
then she's deliberately cheating us.

582
00:25:21,359 --> 00:25:23,160
It cannot be justified no matter where she goes.

583
00:25:25,319 --> 00:25:26,359
You are right, Mother.

584
00:26:01,920 --> 00:26:02,920
Nanny Liu!

585
00:26:04,880 --> 00:26:05,839
Fifth Miss.

586
00:26:05,880 --> 00:26:06,599
Time to go?

587
00:26:07,319 --> 00:26:08,839
Wait a while longer.

588
00:26:08,880 --> 00:26:10,640
Then let's have the meal.

589
00:26:10,680 --> 00:26:12,479
Wait a while longer.

590
00:26:21,719 --> 00:26:23,160
I'm starving.

591
00:26:23,160 --> 00:26:24,359
Brew the “Seven Treasures Thunder” tea

592
00:26:24,359 --> 00:26:25,239
for me to drink.

593
00:26:26,520 --> 00:26:29,119
Miss, why not have some cakes first?

594
00:26:29,199 --> 00:26:30,119
The kitchen has some

595
00:26:30,119 --> 00:26:31,800
new quality pastries today.

596
00:26:31,800 --> 00:26:33,680
You are talking too much!

597
00:26:33,719 --> 00:26:35,160
Go now!

598
00:26:55,920 --> 00:26:57,239
Are you here to call for me?

599
00:26:57,319 --> 00:26:58,599
Come! Bring my cloak now.

600
00:27:01,239 --> 00:27:03,199
I asked the maid servants in the front hall.

601
00:27:03,280 --> 00:27:04,839
After the Countess left Big Madam's court,

602
00:27:04,839 --> 00:27:06,839
she went to the front sitting room.

603
00:27:06,920 --> 00:27:08,239
I took a look,

604
00:27:08,239 --> 00:27:10,520
and saw her son talking to our Second Master.

605
00:27:10,520 --> 00:27:11,719
I fear the mother and son

606
00:27:11,719 --> 00:27:13,280
are leaving soon.

607
00:27:13,400 --> 00:27:14,959
What?

608
00:27:16,239 --> 00:27:17,199
Looks like Big Madam

609
00:27:17,239 --> 00:27:19,400
will not summon you to see the Countess.

610
00:27:24,959 --> 00:27:26,959
Miss…this…

611
00:27:31,719 --> 00:27:34,359
No propriety at all!

612
00:27:35,000 --> 00:27:36,319
You are of marriageable age,

613
00:27:36,319 --> 00:27:38,560
but it's Big Madam who is responsible for such matters.

614
00:27:38,760 --> 00:27:40,599
She has been jealous and hating us for many years!

615
00:27:40,599 --> 00:27:41,400
I wonder how much suffering

616
00:27:41,400 --> 00:27:42,680
you will receive in the future!

617
00:27:42,920 --> 00:27:44,199
You start breaking things now.

618
00:27:44,199 --> 00:27:45,760
I wonder if there would be enough things in this house

619
00:27:45,760 --> 00:27:47,119
for you to squander in the future?

620
00:27:47,439 --> 00:27:48,880
Now what? Should we just not go

621
00:27:48,880 --> 00:27:50,040
because she didn't call us?

622
00:27:50,079 --> 00:27:50,760
You!

623
00:27:50,800 --> 00:27:52,079
I have an idea

624
00:27:52,079 --> 00:27:53,199
though it may not help much,

625
00:27:53,400 --> 00:27:55,160
but at least we've tried.

626
00:27:55,239 --> 00:27:56,160
Fourth Miss,

627
00:27:56,160 --> 00:27:57,400
you should go and take a look.

628
00:27:57,439 --> 00:27:58,680
Even if you can't meet him,

629
00:27:58,680 --> 00:28:00,160
you can at least have a look through the seams.

630
00:28:01,040 --> 00:28:02,199
If you know

631
00:28:02,239 --> 00:28:03,359
what the Countess looks like,

632
00:28:03,439 --> 00:28:04,800
then if there are any banquets

633
00:28:04,800 --> 00:28:06,479
or polo games, poem gatherings, flower viewings in the future,

634
00:28:06,520 --> 00:28:08,119
then you will know who she is.

635
00:28:08,160 --> 00:28:09,479
If you need to try to gain her favor,

636
00:28:09,560 --> 00:28:11,439
then you'll at least have some information.

637
00:28:11,479 --> 00:28:12,640
It's just that our Fourth Miss

638
00:28:12,640 --> 00:28:14,079
will have to suffer some grievances.

639
00:28:18,040 --> 00:28:20,079
As the Fourth Miss,

640
00:28:20,119 --> 00:28:21,319
now do I have to go via the back hall,

641
00:28:21,319 --> 00:28:22,959
and peek from behind the screen?

642
00:28:24,359 --> 00:28:26,119
This is such a disgrace.

643
00:28:26,520 --> 00:28:27,760
Miss, this is not the right way to look at it.

644
00:28:27,800 --> 00:28:29,199
What's so disgraceful about that?

645
00:28:29,319 --> 00:28:30,680
If you don't act when you need to

646
00:28:30,680 --> 00:28:31,719
then even your innards

647
00:28:31,719 --> 00:28:33,920
will turn green from regret!

648
00:28:37,199 --> 00:28:38,599
You should be glad that I asked you

649
00:28:38,599 --> 00:28:40,040
to make embroideries for me.

650
00:28:40,920 --> 00:28:41,839
In any case, if you don't finish

651
00:28:41,839 --> 00:28:43,239
the knee pad in time that I want to give to Eldest Sister,

652
00:28:43,680 --> 00:28:44,920
I won't let you off.

653
00:28:45,760 --> 00:28:47,439
It's what Madam wanted you to embroider

654
00:28:47,439 --> 00:28:49,040
yet you pushed it to me.

655
00:28:49,040 --> 00:28:50,560
I really can't do it.

656
00:28:51,319 --> 00:28:52,400
Why don't we go

657
00:28:52,400 --> 00:28:53,959
and discuss this with Madam then?

658
00:28:54,520 --> 00:28:55,319
Of course we can't

659
00:28:55,359 --> 00:28:57,040
discuss this with my mother!

660
00:28:57,119 --> 00:28:58,640
What's wrong with you?

661
00:28:58,640 --> 00:29:00,040
I told you to help me with some embroidery,

662
00:29:00,040 --> 00:29:02,079
but you're making so many excuses.

663
00:29:02,319 --> 00:29:03,119
I don't care.

664
00:29:03,160 --> 00:29:04,880
You must embroider this knee pad.

665
00:29:04,880 --> 00:29:06,199
If you fail to do it…

666
00:29:07,040 --> 00:29:08,359
If you fail to do it…

667
00:29:09,280 --> 00:29:11,760
At meal time, I'll personally make

668
00:29:11,760 --> 00:29:14,560
barbecued lamb and charcoal-grilled meat.

669
00:29:14,640 --> 00:29:16,239
Really?

670
00:29:16,280 --> 00:29:18,520
Stop interrupting!

671
00:29:18,520 --> 00:29:19,599
I want to eat that

672
00:29:19,599 --> 00:29:20,640
but also…

673
00:29:20,719 --> 00:29:22,359
I want that knee pad too!

674
00:29:22,359 --> 00:29:24,280
Moreover, do it fast.

675
00:29:24,280 --> 00:29:27,479
Y-You want me to copy books,

676
00:29:27,520 --> 00:29:29,000
and want me to cook lunch too.

677
00:29:29,000 --> 00:29:31,599
And you want to me make knee pads.

678
00:29:32,880 --> 00:29:34,920
I-I can't do it all.

679
00:29:34,959 --> 00:29:37,479
I'll just let you

680
00:29:37,479 --> 00:29:39,359
go to see the Madam and reports.

681
00:29:39,439 --> 00:29:40,959
I won't do them all.

682
00:29:42,880 --> 00:29:43,839
Why don't we go

683
00:29:43,839 --> 00:29:45,040
and eat the lamb first?

684
00:29:45,079 --> 00:29:46,439
My stomach's already growling,

685
00:29:46,439 --> 00:29:47,199
I'm starving.

686
00:29:47,319 --> 00:29:48,880
Cook it fast.

687
00:29:48,959 --> 00:29:50,199
You should make me an extra knee pad

688
00:29:50,199 --> 00:29:52,680
for every quarter-hour of delay!

689
00:29:52,680 --> 00:29:54,160
Let's go!

690
00:29:55,280 --> 00:29:56,839
Miss.

691
00:30:03,800 --> 00:30:05,119
Miss, be careful.

692
00:30:05,160 --> 00:30:06,000
It's such a big step!

693
00:30:06,000 --> 00:30:08,079
Why didn't you watch out for me?

694
00:30:08,160 --> 00:30:09,359
You let everyone see this.

695
00:30:09,359 --> 00:30:10,439
Come with me.

696
00:30:10,439 --> 00:30:11,199
Miss, be careful.

697
00:30:22,839 --> 00:30:24,479
Why is she behaving furtively?

698
00:30:24,959 --> 00:30:26,319
Let's follow her.

699
00:30:27,520 --> 00:30:29,040
Let's go.

700
00:30:29,040 --> 00:30:30,359
Don't go.

701
00:30:32,920 --> 00:30:34,800
I… I need to go back and make barbecued lamb.

702
00:30:35,119 --> 00:30:36,359
She's behaving furtively.

703
00:30:36,439 --> 00:30:37,520
She must be up to some tricks.

704
00:30:37,520 --> 00:30:38,640
Let's go and take a look.

705
00:30:38,640 --> 00:30:39,439
We should…

706
00:30:39,439 --> 00:30:40,680
go back and eat the lamb!

707
00:30:40,800 --> 00:30:42,640
I'm not eating that anymore!

708
00:30:42,640 --> 00:30:43,400
You…

709
00:30:43,599 --> 00:30:44,359
Let me tell you.

710
00:30:44,359 --> 00:30:44,839
If you go with me,

711
00:30:45,239 --> 00:30:45,800
you don't have to

712
00:30:45,800 --> 00:30:46,760
make those knee pads for me!

713
00:30:46,800 --> 00:30:47,640
Let's go now.

714
00:30:47,680 --> 00:30:49,239
I must catch her on something!

715
00:30:49,239 --> 00:30:49,800
Hurry up.

716
00:30:49,800 --> 00:30:50,680
Hurry up.

717
00:31:15,599 --> 00:31:18,040
Fifth Sister, who do you see that is out there?

718
00:31:27,199 --> 00:31:29,000
I haven't finished copying the Songs of Chu

719
00:31:29,000 --> 00:31:29,880
that Scholar Zhuang assigned me.

720
00:31:29,880 --> 00:31:30,640
I'm leaving first.

721
00:31:30,719 --> 00:31:31,520
Come back.

722
00:31:42,760 --> 00:31:43,719
Sixth Sister, who you think

723
00:31:44,599 --> 00:31:46,359
Is better between the Young Lord

724
00:31:46,359 --> 00:31:47,839
and the Sixth Son of the Wus House?

725
00:31:49,880 --> 00:31:51,760
Whoever Scholar Zhuang thinks is better,

726
00:31:51,760 --> 00:31:52,719
then he is better.

727
00:31:57,800 --> 00:31:59,319
Classes start at the second quarter of six in the morning.

728
00:31:59,959 --> 00:32:01,839
We study a new text every five days.

729
00:32:02,119 --> 00:32:03,880
Starting at six in the morning!

730
00:32:05,520 --> 00:32:06,839
Young Lord,

731
00:32:06,839 --> 00:32:09,000
how do you manage to get up?

732
00:32:10,000 --> 00:32:12,959
The Sheng family has a younger daughter. She also…

733
00:32:15,079 --> 00:32:16,520
Who?

734
00:32:21,000 --> 00:32:23,040
Frankly, it's difficult for me

735
00:32:23,040 --> 00:32:24,199
to get up at this time.

736
00:32:25,680 --> 00:32:27,400
Brother Qi, Brother Qi,

737
00:32:27,400 --> 00:32:28,680
why do you bother this?

738
00:32:28,719 --> 00:32:30,760
We are from aristocratic families.

739
00:32:30,800 --> 00:32:32,280
You are talented and ambitious

740
00:32:32,319 --> 00:32:33,520
and set on taking the examinations.

741
00:32:33,560 --> 00:32:35,640
As for me, I'll just wait to inherit my title.

742
00:32:37,839 --> 00:32:39,319
They all say that the Sixth Son of Liangs

743
00:32:39,319 --> 00:32:41,280
is very respectable and noble,

744
00:32:42,599 --> 00:32:44,439
but words are pale against meeting the actual person.

745
00:32:45,040 --> 00:32:46,800
In my opinion

746
00:32:46,800 --> 00:32:47,920
he's like that Second Uncle Gu,

747
00:32:47,920 --> 00:32:49,479
just an idle wastrel.

748
00:32:50,640 --> 00:32:51,439
In view of

749
00:32:51,439 --> 00:32:52,719
the noble young masters in Bianliang,

750
00:32:53,160 --> 00:32:55,319
and in terms of talents and looks,

751
00:32:56,920 --> 00:32:58,160
Fifth Sister,

752
00:32:58,160 --> 00:32:59,599
which do you think is better?

753
00:33:02,640 --> 00:33:04,359
Fourth Sister, the way you talk about this,

754
00:33:04,520 --> 00:33:07,119
It sounds like you are a princess or

755
00:33:07,199 --> 00:33:09,719
a concubine in the palace

756
00:33:09,719 --> 00:33:11,839
and all the noble Young Masters in Bianliang

757
00:33:11,839 --> 00:33:13,160
are there for your picking.

758
00:33:14,119 --> 00:33:15,280
It's a pity that

759
00:33:15,280 --> 00:33:16,800
no matter how high your ambition is,

760
00:33:17,280 --> 00:33:18,439
you'll never be in the same class

761
00:33:18,479 --> 00:33:19,719
as the Duke Qi.

762
00:33:24,119 --> 00:33:26,079
It's not proper for young ladies

763
00:33:26,079 --> 00:33:27,160
to peek into the front halls.

764
00:33:27,439 --> 00:33:29,079
We should go back.

765
00:33:29,119 --> 00:33:30,680
That's right.

766
00:33:30,680 --> 00:33:32,239
Little Sister is the respectable child of main wife

767
00:33:32,239 --> 00:33:33,599
and naturally should be the most well-behaved.

768
00:33:34,040 --> 00:33:35,439
But what's the use of being well-behaved?

769
00:33:35,839 --> 00:33:36,680
You can't even have a chat

770
00:33:36,680 --> 00:33:39,000
with Brother Yuanruo!

771
00:33:39,040 --> 00:33:39,920
What a waste of Madam's efforts

772
00:33:39,959 --> 00:33:41,599
in sending you to school.

773
00:33:42,319 --> 00:33:44,319
Forget about composing poems or literary works.

774
00:33:44,400 --> 00:33:45,839
I'm afraid you can't even differentiate

775
00:33:45,839 --> 00:33:47,599
between Confucius and Mencius.

776
00:33:47,640 --> 00:33:48,839
If people didn't know better,

777
00:33:48,839 --> 00:33:50,239
they'd think she's the daughter of the concubine.

778
00:33:50,239 --> 00:33:51,959
What are you talking about?

779
00:33:54,680 --> 00:33:55,680
Fifth Sister, Sixth Sister,

780
00:33:55,680 --> 00:33:57,839
what are you doing?

781
00:34:09,639 --> 00:34:10,639
What's wrong? What happened?

782
00:34:18,560 --> 00:34:19,959
I… I was going to leave.

783
00:34:22,439 --> 00:34:24,080
Where are your manners?

784
00:34:49,600 --> 00:34:51,520
I heard she was the legitimate daughter.

785
00:34:52,959 --> 00:34:54,439
I've never seen any daughter of any other house

786
00:34:54,439 --> 00:34:55,560
show her face like that!

787
00:34:58,320 --> 00:35:00,120
Minister Sheng is a true gentleman.

788
00:35:00,159 --> 00:35:01,320
Old Madam of Sheng House

789
00:35:01,320 --> 00:35:02,679
is the precious daughter of a marquis.

790
00:35:02,879 --> 00:35:05,360
Their family has always kept up with rigorous manners.

791
00:35:05,360 --> 00:35:06,760
I never ever imagined that.

792
00:35:08,120 --> 00:35:10,280
Don't play so innocent now.

793
00:35:10,320 --> 00:35:11,719
Those maidens.

794
00:35:11,719 --> 00:35:13,159
If it hadn't been because they knew you were coming,

795
00:35:13,159 --> 00:35:14,760
and they wanted to steal a look,

796
00:35:14,760 --> 00:35:16,959
this wouldn't have happened.

797
00:35:18,120 --> 00:35:19,600
The daughters of Sheng House were just too anxious

798
00:35:19,639 --> 00:35:22,879
and made an ignorant blunder.

799
00:35:24,080 --> 00:35:25,000
The one on the side

800
00:35:25,000 --> 00:35:27,239
seemed quite gentle and refined.

801
00:35:27,280 --> 00:35:28,600
She seemed to have been dragged there

802
00:35:28,600 --> 00:35:30,159
forcibly by the two on the ground.

803
00:35:30,239 --> 00:35:31,639
From her manners of speaking,

804
00:35:31,639 --> 00:35:34,000
she seems to be a concubine-born.

805
00:35:34,040 --> 00:35:36,159
That's not an issue!

806
00:35:36,239 --> 00:35:37,280
Treating concubine's daughters harshly

807
00:35:37,280 --> 00:35:40,320
is the conduct of unrefined lowly households!

808
00:35:41,719 --> 00:35:42,919
Once a woman marries out,

809
00:35:42,919 --> 00:35:44,760
it's a new world.

810
00:35:44,760 --> 00:35:46,159
As long as they are not married yet,

811
00:35:46,159 --> 00:35:48,520
no one knows what the future holds.

812
00:36:02,159 --> 00:36:03,959
Young Master, only you can smile about it.

813
00:36:08,679 --> 00:36:09,800
I don't know why,

814
00:36:11,600 --> 00:36:13,120
but I was angry at her

815
00:36:13,120 --> 00:36:14,120
for many days.

816
00:36:15,399 --> 00:36:17,159
Yet as soon as I saw her,

817
00:36:17,320 --> 00:36:18,560
I found it amusing again.

818
00:36:19,520 --> 00:36:21,760
She's always lost and dazed,

819
00:36:21,760 --> 00:36:23,239
or dodging and evading.

820
00:36:23,600 --> 00:36:25,000
She's not inclined for others to see her.

821
00:36:25,000 --> 00:36:26,479
When have you ever seen her like today?

822
00:36:27,879 --> 00:36:29,520
Indeed quite pitiful and cute.

823
00:36:29,520 --> 00:36:31,639
I won't forget it in ten years.

824
00:36:32,760 --> 00:36:34,239
Quieter, Young Master.

825
00:36:34,239 --> 00:36:35,879
Don't let the driver outside hear you.

826
00:36:35,919 --> 00:36:36,879
Why?

827
00:36:36,879 --> 00:36:38,399
When the Sheng maidens

828
00:36:38,399 --> 00:36:39,399
fell down today,

829
00:36:39,439 --> 00:36:40,719
you wanted to help her up.

830
00:36:40,719 --> 00:36:41,879
It's not proper.

831
00:36:41,879 --> 00:36:43,080
What's not proper about it?

832
00:36:44,360 --> 00:36:46,399
I've been hiding it for you all this time,

833
00:36:46,399 --> 00:36:47,879
but thankfully Sixth Miss understands propriety.

834
00:36:48,280 --> 00:36:49,679
Even though you insist on getting close to her,

835
00:36:50,120 --> 00:36:51,439
she's not spoiled or arrogant,

836
00:36:51,439 --> 00:36:52,520
or else it would be hard to hide it.

837
00:36:56,399 --> 00:36:58,199
What's there to hide?

838
00:36:58,239 --> 00:37:00,000
Your mother won't like your conduct.

839
00:37:00,000 --> 00:37:00,800
And today we had Countess of Yongchang

840
00:37:00,800 --> 00:37:02,760
along too.

841
00:37:02,879 --> 00:37:03,879
She's got quite a tongue.

842
00:37:05,719 --> 00:37:07,479
If word gets out that

843
00:37:07,479 --> 00:37:08,840
you helped Miss Sheng up,

844
00:37:08,840 --> 00:37:09,840
then it would be all real.

845
00:37:10,199 --> 00:37:11,479
If your mother finds out,

846
00:37:11,479 --> 00:37:13,600
she'll definitely come to the Shengs' Manor.

847
00:37:14,360 --> 00:37:15,679
If she shows up at the door,

848
00:37:15,679 --> 00:37:16,719
the Sheng Misses would be obliged

849
00:37:16,719 --> 00:37:17,639
to answer her one by one.

850
00:37:17,679 --> 00:37:18,360
Who knows what

851
00:37:18,399 --> 00:37:19,439
she would ask?

852
00:37:20,639 --> 00:37:21,760
Your conduct in the past

853
00:37:21,760 --> 00:37:22,840
would all be exposed!

854
00:37:24,600 --> 00:37:25,959
Look at how scared you are.

855
00:37:26,320 --> 00:37:27,760
I didn't help her up today.

856
00:37:28,840 --> 00:37:30,159
Moreover,

857
00:37:30,159 --> 00:37:31,479
Mother would disdain the Sheng family's

858
00:37:32,080 --> 00:37:33,879
social status.

859
00:37:33,879 --> 00:37:34,959
She wouldn't go there.

860
00:37:35,199 --> 00:37:36,560
You never know.

861
00:37:36,560 --> 00:37:37,560
For your sake,

862
00:37:37,560 --> 00:37:39,199
Your mother is watching everything closely.

863
00:37:39,479 --> 00:37:41,520
And the Duke is concerned.

864
00:37:42,800 --> 00:37:43,560
Every night he returns,

865
00:37:43,560 --> 00:37:44,800
he asks about everything.

866
00:37:44,800 --> 00:37:46,239
What's there to ask?

867
00:37:46,840 --> 00:37:50,120
The Sixth Sheng Miss

868
00:37:50,120 --> 00:37:51,800
is only just short of sweeping me out the door.

869
00:37:57,719 --> 00:37:58,520
What did you do wrongly?

870
00:38:01,560 --> 00:38:04,159
I shouldn't have . . .

871
00:38:04,600 --> 00:38:06,159
I shouldn't have, without summoning,

872
00:38:08,959 --> 00:38:10,520
barged into the front hall.

873
00:38:12,360 --> 00:38:13,879
What summoning?

874
00:38:14,719 --> 00:38:16,280
Is there a place in this house

875
00:38:16,280 --> 00:38:18,320
that the daughter can't go?

876
00:38:18,639 --> 00:38:20,280
Are we still Shengs?

877
00:38:20,600 --> 00:38:22,439
You just beat me when you want to.

878
00:38:22,959 --> 00:38:23,560
But why do you just favor me

879
00:38:23,560 --> 00:38:24,439
and ignore the other two?

880
00:38:24,800 --> 00:38:26,280
As to going to the front hall,

881
00:38:26,280 --> 00:38:27,800
we all three went there.

882
00:38:27,840 --> 00:38:29,360
Why is it only the two of us got beaten

883
00:38:29,439 --> 00:38:30,439
and not Molan?

884
00:38:31,840 --> 00:38:33,399
What?

885
00:38:33,399 --> 00:38:34,479
Sister is right.

886
00:38:35,760 --> 00:38:37,679
Since Eldest Sister married off,

887
00:38:38,320 --> 00:38:40,760
I am the eldest among the daughters still at home.

888
00:38:41,399 --> 00:38:42,280
But I failed to look after

889
00:38:42,280 --> 00:38:43,719
my younger sisters well today and let

890
00:38:43,800 --> 00:38:45,199
this disaster occur,

891
00:38:45,199 --> 00:38:47,000
and I ask Father to punish me too.

892
00:38:47,199 --> 00:38:48,919
We don't need you to speak here!

893
00:38:49,040 --> 00:38:50,280
Yes, yes, yes.

894
00:38:50,280 --> 00:38:52,600
Madam, don't be angry.

895
00:38:52,639 --> 00:38:55,840
Mo'er, this has nothing to do with you.

896
00:38:55,840 --> 00:38:57,520
You get up.

897
00:38:58,919 --> 00:39:00,479
What?

898
00:39:02,959 --> 00:39:03,760
You don't feel

899
00:39:03,800 --> 00:39:06,000
should be getting this?

900
00:39:06,760 --> 00:39:08,679
Give me your hand.

901
00:39:09,360 --> 00:39:11,479
Your hand!

902
00:39:20,520 --> 00:39:22,360
Your hand again!

903
00:39:28,159 --> 00:39:29,239
If I don't punish you harshly,

904
00:39:29,239 --> 00:39:30,000
you just don't know

905
00:39:30,000 --> 00:39:32,360
where you erred.

906
00:39:33,239 --> 00:39:36,479
You're punishing us for barging into the front hall.

907
00:39:37,280 --> 00:39:39,080
Breaking the family rules,

908
00:39:39,080 --> 00:39:40,520
and you blame us for falling down

909
00:39:40,520 --> 00:39:41,560
and startling the guests.

910
00:39:41,879 --> 00:39:43,919
Bringing shame to Sheng's honor.

911
00:39:43,959 --> 00:39:45,239
But it was Molan who brought us

912
00:39:45,280 --> 00:39:47,520
to the front hall!

913
00:39:47,600 --> 00:39:49,399
And it was Molan who pushed us to get us falling down!

914
00:39:49,479 --> 00:39:50,600
We were just going to have a chat

915
00:39:50,600 --> 00:39:52,439
behind the screen,

916
00:39:52,439 --> 00:39:53,719
just a chat, we never…

917
00:39:53,800 --> 00:39:54,760
I saw that Fifth and Sixth Sister

918
00:39:54,800 --> 00:39:57,040
were walking ahead,

919
00:39:57,239 --> 00:40:00,280
and I just wanted to startle them for fun.

920
00:40:00,320 --> 00:40:03,000
Ultimately, I am the eldest sister

921
00:40:03,040 --> 00:40:05,360
and I failed to watch over them well.

922
00:40:05,360 --> 00:40:08,320
Father please punish me along with them.

923
00:40:11,040 --> 00:40:13,280
You're lying! You're lying!

924
00:40:13,360 --> 00:40:13,959
It was clear

925
00:40:13,959 --> 00:40:15,959
that you who took us to the front hall.

926
00:40:16,040 --> 00:40:18,679
Sixth Sister, say something!

927
00:40:21,080 --> 00:40:23,760
Speak! What are you doing just looking?

928
00:40:23,760 --> 00:40:26,800
Ming'er, you tell the truth.

929
00:40:26,800 --> 00:40:28,600
What happened?

930
00:40:31,840 --> 00:40:34,280
Say it!

931
00:40:34,280 --> 00:40:37,879
It…was Fourth Sister.

932
00:40:37,959 --> 00:40:40,439
She went before us.

933
00:40:41,479 --> 00:40:42,439
Little Sister!

934
00:40:42,719 --> 00:40:44,159
How is that you're being forced by Fifth Sister

935
00:40:44,159 --> 00:40:45,399
to talk nonsense?

936
00:40:46,919 --> 00:40:48,399
How did I force her?

937
00:40:49,320 --> 00:40:51,360
She's clearly telling the truth!

938
00:40:52,679 --> 00:40:54,919
I was indeed with the sisters.

939
00:40:55,959 --> 00:40:57,760
My sisters committed a mistake.

940
00:40:58,280 --> 00:41:00,560
I failed to manage them well.

941
00:41:03,600 --> 00:41:05,439
May Father punish me, too.

942
00:41:05,439 --> 00:41:07,439
so Fifth Sister's pacified.

943
00:41:09,360 --> 00:41:10,679
Look at your sister!

944
00:41:13,600 --> 00:41:16,600
Mo'er, you're more mature than they are.

945
00:41:16,719 --> 00:41:17,879
You're a good child.

946
00:41:17,879 --> 00:41:19,600
You're always thinking of protecting them.

947
00:41:20,040 --> 00:41:20,760
Rise.

948
00:41:21,639 --> 00:41:23,159
Learn from your elder sister!

949
00:41:23,719 --> 00:41:25,399
I'll never learn from her!

950
00:41:25,520 --> 00:41:26,320
The hell with the good child.

951
00:41:26,320 --> 00:41:27,479
She's a liar!

952
00:41:27,520 --> 00:41:30,000
You are lying with her eyes open!

953
00:41:31,840 --> 00:41:33,479
It was clearly your error!

954
00:41:34,320 --> 00:41:35,520
How do you just listen to

955
00:41:35,520 --> 00:41:37,959
that little witch?

956
00:41:38,080 --> 00:41:39,679
You wouldn't listen to a word

957
00:41:39,679 --> 00:41:41,520
my daughter said!

958
00:41:41,520 --> 00:41:43,639
Look at your own daughter!

959
00:41:43,679 --> 00:41:45,919
Didn't you see her just now?

960
00:41:46,000 --> 00:41:47,120
So spoiled by you

961
00:41:47,120 --> 00:41:48,919
that she's lawless now.

962
00:41:49,000 --> 00:41:50,280
You didn't see it?

963
00:41:50,280 --> 00:41:52,520
She was about to beat her!

964
00:41:54,120 --> 00:41:55,439
First, she embarrassed herself

965
00:41:55,439 --> 00:41:56,600
before guests from outside.

966
00:41:56,639 --> 00:41:58,719
Then she plotted to hit her elder sister.

967
00:41:58,760 --> 00:41:59,639
Who knows

968
00:41:59,639 --> 00:42:01,479
what she might do tomorrow!

969
00:42:01,520 --> 00:42:02,280
If I don't punish her now,

970
00:42:02,320 --> 00:42:04,719
when should I?

971
00:42:04,719 --> 00:42:06,919
Should I wait until she commits the gravest mistake?

972
00:42:06,919 --> 00:42:08,600
Then the two of us go before the ancestral hall

973
00:42:08,600 --> 00:42:11,080
and cry to our ancestors?

974
00:42:11,120 --> 00:42:13,800
The two of you were unruly

975
00:42:13,800 --> 00:42:15,639
and startled the guests.

976
00:42:15,639 --> 00:42:17,679
Go kneel in the ancestral shrine!

977
00:42:17,760 --> 00:42:19,399
I didn't do anything wrong.

978
00:42:19,399 --> 00:42:21,360
She is framing me, clearly.

979
00:42:21,399 --> 00:42:23,320
I won't kneel!

980
00:42:23,360 --> 00:42:25,159
You still insist you did nothing wrong?

981
00:42:26,919 --> 00:42:28,520
Even if Mo'er wanted to push you,

982
00:42:28,520 --> 00:42:29,719
you had to be there

983
00:42:29,719 --> 00:42:30,639
to be pushed!

984
00:42:31,879 --> 00:42:32,879
If you had been docile

985
00:42:32,879 --> 00:42:33,919
and staying in your room,

986
00:42:33,919 --> 00:42:34,600
quietly embroidering

987
00:42:34,600 --> 00:42:36,280
and writing at home,

988
00:42:36,320 --> 00:42:37,479
how would she push you?

989
00:42:38,639 --> 00:42:39,600
Isn't it because you erred in

990
00:42:39,600 --> 00:42:41,120
going to the front hall unsummoned in the first place?

991
00:42:42,280 --> 00:42:43,320
Really!

992
00:42:46,439 --> 00:42:48,080
I really didn't do anything wrong.

993
00:42:50,040 --> 00:42:52,040
You're unreasonable, Father.

994
00:42:52,080 --> 00:42:53,000
If I don't punish you well today,

995
00:42:53,000 --> 00:42:55,000
you won't know your mistake!

996
00:42:55,040 --> 00:42:57,719
You still want to hit her?

997
00:43:01,320 --> 00:43:04,280
Do you still insist you're not wrong?

998
00:43:04,320 --> 00:43:05,199
Then go to the shrine

999
00:43:05,199 --> 00:43:06,840
and kneel for three days!

1000
00:43:06,919 --> 00:43:09,080
Reflect thoroughly.
